#, fuzzy, kde-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<p>Select the channel mode of the resulting Mp3 file:\n"
#| "<p><b>Stereo</b><br>\n"
#| "In this mode, the encoder makes no use of potential correlations between "
#| "the two input channels; it can, however, negotiate the bit demand between "
