#| "In this mode, the encoder will make use of correlations between both "
#| "channels. The signal will be matrixed into a sum (\"mid\"), computed by L"
#| "+R, and difference (\"side\") signal, computed by L-R, and more bits are "
#| "allocated to the mid channel. This will effectively increase the "
#| "bandwidth if the signal does not have too much stereo separation, thus "
